{"tid":1968701,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"20 DSE 想入醫科一問","createTime":"2020-04-12T00:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T06:42:34.000Z","uid":210651,"like":1,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"24f3feecfc142424271b8bd10516ab2a5209c1d5","tid":1968701,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:30:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟今年DSE 想入中大醫科，但呢個念頭係去到中六中期先萌生，因為本身諗住頹頹地入Physiotherapy 算，但突然有好大嘅慾望想做醫生救人。（絕對唔關錢事）<br />\n<br />\n我一向成績唔太差，但問題在於中四五都係hea hea地讀，依家睇法應該要考到醫科分數有啲勉強，可能最後28-29分收皮， 所以想問如果炒DSE有冇其他方法之後入翻medic？ lets say 大學trans 系，咁我又應該pick 咩系比較有可能上翻medic， 同GPA requirement要幾多？<br />\n<br />\n我知我試都未考就咁樣諗好on9，但真係好心急想知，唔該各位大佬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6598948d82c652a55746bed3735939e5eb2233","tid":1968701,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:31:15.000Z","msg":"補充，屋企家境普通，住公屋，唔會有錢出國讀書。"},{"pid":"25ad9267c29d166055bba4bd3964fe9c7b324fac","tid":1968701,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:31:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d35bac6162d917cdb962eb513b5e1ee8e4573110","tid":1968701,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"868c04d47a53cc587ca9614f09f113001935aa9f","tid":1968701,"uid":102187,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:33:37.000Z","msg":"有<br />\ncu biomedical 爆gpa trans cu med<br />\n每年都有一兩個"},{"pid":"6d41f45281189b8145ebbc1cd466ee43376e9d1d","tid":1968701,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"唔知香港點<br />\n不過外國做community 就<br />\n1. amoxil 1 tds<br />\n2. keflex 2 bd<br />\n計錯數出錯藥都大把<br />\n<br />\n想救人大把出路啦，我都諗緊quit鳩份濕鳩工<br />\n<br />\nb.pharm usyd."},{"pid":"6a610c531c8b48f132dd582ec41e8ba65ae94040","tid":1968701,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d35bac6162d917cdb962eb513b5e1ee8e4573110","tid